    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2>Advocacy</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 about">
            	<p></p>
                <p>I’m making tech inclusive and accessible to <em>all</em> women through education, collaboration, and code. By teaching and collaborating with under-served women and fostering honest conversations about diversity, I am dedicated towards creating a trans-inclusive tech community for women. Through my contributions to open source software, education and impactful organizations, my skills and dedication create positive change in social issues that I am passionate about.</p>
                <a href="#">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

